data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this spacious single family home with four oversized bedroom and very large backyard. This home has a very elegant style that will provide plenty of space to entertain your family or group of friends while you prep your food in your spacious kitchen countertop. Another great reason to make an offer soon is that all appliances, A/C, water heater, roof was installed only five years ago This home will not last very long as it is priced to sell based on having an oversized lot and huge bedrooms.
